Hello guys ! (sorry for my bad english)

Today I show you my new map, mg_fun_boat. It's an only cut map (not a knife area, because it is on a boat, and there is a disco...). You have to just kill your enemies ^^. I made the boat (not a prefab).

In the disco, the music is "Michael Mind - Feel Your Body".

HAVE FUN ! (I made this map in 4 hours, so I know it's not UNBELIEVABLE !).

Visit : www.niko-mapping-studio.tk
